'''亚硫酸银'''是银的[[亚硫酸盐|亚硫酸盐]]，[[化学式|化学式]] Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub>。这种不稳定的物质在加热或光照下会[[分解|分解]]成[[连二硫酸银|连二硫酸银]]和[[硫酸银|硫酸银]]。<ref name=hpic>{{cite book|title = Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry|volume = 2|editor-first = Georg|editor-last = Brauer|year = 1965|publisher = [[Academic_Press|Academic Press Inc.]]|place = New York|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Pef47TK5NfkC&pg=PA1043|page = 1043|isbn = 0323161294|access-date = 2021-03-20|archive-date = 2020-07-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200730152052/https://books.google.com/books?id=Pef47TK5NfkC&pg=PA1043}}</ref>

==制备==
亚硫酸银可以由[[硝酸银|硝酸银]]和[[亚硫酸钠|亚硫酸钠]]反应沉淀：
:2 AgNO<sub>3</sub> + Na<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub> {{eqm}} Ag<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>3</sub> + 2 NaNO<sub>3</sub>

沉淀后，过滤亚硫酸银，用沸水将其洗涤，然后在[[真空|真空]]中干燥。 <ref name=hpic />

